            "screenshots": [
                "https://xedqdxjorneezfnpyogg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/plugin-screenshots/8c62b89f-94b9-4aa6-9c86-34aa86e55b58/image_2026-06-01_132325933.png",
                "https://xedqdxjorneezfnpyogg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/plugin-screenshots/c4fd9e02-8c87-42f6-9d3b-6b109ec998c8/image_2026-06-01_132336861.png",
                "https://xedqdxjorneezfnpyogg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/plugin-screenshots/51d32926-3339-4b18-b63c-a8b0990eb1df/image_2026-06-01_132347149.png",
                "https://xedqdxjorneezfnpyogg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/plugin-screenshots/a532b08d-b760-4dce-afc0-eb983c33e0dc/image_2026-06-01_132401094.png",
                "https://xedqdxjorneezfnpyogg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/plugin-screenshots/af140af5-f42f-425f-825e-ed2c60d1db5e/image_2026-06-01_132407502.png",
                "https://xedqdxjorneezfnpyogg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/plugin-screenshots/c83cf76e-9f68-4cc8-947e-df2e5ea21737/image_2026-06-01_132431256.png",
                "https://xedqdxjorneezfnpyogg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/plugin-screenshots/506e49a3-f9fe-4b10-bd40-838f44d27eae/image_2026-06-01_132445069.png"
            ],
            "website_url": null,
            "download_url": "https://xedqdxjorneezfnpyogg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/plugin-jars/12368a70-c898-4266-ae37-eecd0843d2b3/1780459596256-GamemodePlugin.jar",
            "jar_filename": "GamemodePlugin.jar",
            "long_description": "**GamemodePlugin** is a lightweight, high-performance Minecraft plugin designed to make gamemode switching fast, simple, and painless for both players and staff.\n\nBuilt with usability and efficiency in mind, it provides a clean command system for switching between Survival, Creative, Adventure, and Spectator modes without the usual clutter or confusion. Whether you're moderating a server, building massive projects, or just managing gameplay flow, GamemodePlugin gives you instant control right when you need it.\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://discord.carnagemc.net\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5ac8884b3c4916cbac2b514220b9bb678db039b7.png\" width=\"300\">\n  </a>\n  <br>\n  <i>Please join the Discord if you have questions!</i>\n</p>\n\nIt includes fully tab-completed commands, so you don’t have to remember long syntax or deal with errors from typos. Just type `/gamemode` and you’re already halfway done. The plugin also supports shorthand inputs like `s`, `c`, `a`, and `sp`, making switching modes even faster for experienced users.\n\nStaff-friendly features ensure smooth server management, including optional player targeting so you can change your own gamemode or switch someone else’s with a single command. Permissions are structured cleanly, so server owners can easily control who has access to each gamemode or admin-level command.\n\nGamemodePlugin is optimized for modern Minecraft versions and built to be lag-free, reliable, and plug-and-play. No bloated features, no unnecessary extras—just a solid core system that does exactly what it should do, and does it well.\n\nIf you want a clean, old-school style utility plugin that respects simplicity while still feeling modern and polished, GamemodePlugin fits right in.\n\n# Folia\n\nFolia is coming soon so stay updated."
        },
