                "https://xedqdxjorneezfnpyogg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/plugin-screenshots/a9ff5e2f-cad4-4805-9acd-095065d18179/c76ad87e-3b49-427d-8210-09dffb5ee576/1782881136890.png",
                "https://xedqdxjorneezfnpyogg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/plugin-screenshots/a9ff5e2f-cad4-4805-9acd-095065d18179/c76ad87e-3b49-427d-8210-09dffb5ee576/1782881146344.png",
                "https://xedqdxjorneezfnpyogg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/plugin-screenshots/a9ff5e2f-cad4-4805-9acd-095065d18179/c76ad87e-3b49-427d-8210-09dffb5ee576/1782881170017.png",
                "https://xedqdxjorneezfnpyogg.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/plugin-screenshots/a9ff5e2f-cad4-4805-9acd-095065d18179/c76ad87e-3b49-427d-8210-09dffb5ee576/1782881183360.png"
            ],
            "website_url": "https://carnagemc.net",
            "download_url": null,
            "jar_filename": "RankManager-1.0.4.jar",
            "long_description": "**RankManager** is a lightweight yet powerful Minecraft plugin designed to make rank and permission management fast, simple, and efficient for server owners and staff.\n\nBuilt with usability in mind, RankManager provides a clean command system for managing player ranks without complicated setup or confusing syntax. Whether you’re running a small SMP or a large network, RankManager gives you full control over rank management exactly when you need it.\n\n\nCommands:\n```\n/rank <player> <rank>\n/rank create <group>\n/rank delete <group>\n/rank reload\n/removerank <player> <rank>\n/ranks\n```\n\n# IMPORTANT\n**RankManager** needs to use **[LuckPerms](https://carnagemc.net/modrinth-plugins/9eGKb6K1)** for ranks\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://discord.carnagemc.net\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5ac8884b3c4916cbac2b514220b9bb678db039b7.png\" width=\"300\">\n  </a>\n  <br>\n  <i>Please join the Discord if you have questions!</i>\n</p>\n\nUsing **/rank**, staff can quickly assign ranks to players in seconds. Need to remove a rank? **/removerank** handles that instantly. You can also view all available ranks using **/ranks**, making it easy to stay organized and keep track of your server’s rank structure.\n\nRankManager also includes permission management through **/perm**, allowing administrators to assign, modify, and control permissions with ease. This ensures you can fine-tune what each rank or player has access to without digging through complicated configuration files.\n\nStaff-friendly features help streamline moderation and server management, reducing time spent on repetitive tasks. Permissions are structured cleanly, giving server owners precise control over who can assign ranks, remove ranks, or manage permission nodes.\n\nRankManager is optimized for modern Minecraft versions and built to be reliable, fast, and easy to use. No bloated extras—just a polished rank management system that does exactly what it’s designed to do."
        },
